{
  "stem": "6773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As soon as they-- they-- let me go back to the-- as soon as they took my-- my-- my friend away, the whole group fall apart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nothing anybody could plan because everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had-- in-- in-- in-- in the camp, we had, not many, but individuals which used to go out to the Gestapo and tell them what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would squeal on us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how the Gestapo I found out what and when, but after-- after this incident, we lost everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had connections with Gentile on the outside of the ghetto, the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the people they were waiting for us to get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there on, they would connect us to some kind of organization which were at the forests.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when they took them away, there was no people which could make any plans because everything was too fresh.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then in three or four months later, they took us all together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they sent us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
